    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

    <div class="faq">
      <h3>What age group is the academy for?</h3>
      <p>The Skills Development Course is designed for children aged 10–15 years.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq">
      <h3>Can beginners join the academy?</h3>
      <p>Yes! Our program is suitable for complete beginners and those with prior boxing experience.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq">
      <h3>How does the level system work?</h3>
      <p>There are 7 progressive levels. Each includes 12 weekly sessions and a grading day to assess skills and readiness for the next stage.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq">
      <h3>What does the enrolment fee include?</h3>
      <p>The £20 enrolment fee covers registration and admin for each level. The £40 grading fee includes your assessment, level certificate, and new club t-shirt or vest.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq">
      <h3>Where do I sign up?</h3>
